{"tid":599432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"13歲港中一女生收$3000  胸圍藏毒闖澳門被捕","createTime":"2018-03-20T11:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T21:13:58.000Z","uid":28366,"like":101,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"bc2813899ab1cdf4dba48e3d964a265b69fae9bb","tid":599432,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T11:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/195029_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F195029_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f09ed1d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/195033_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F195033_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7781ee33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名13歲中一女生為3000元報酬，利用胸圍藏毒入境澳門當場被截。澳門司警昨日偵破該宗跨境販毒案，案中同時拘捕2名18和19歲的香港少年，其中1人亦為學生。行動中，司警共檢獲近60克可卡因，黑市價19萬澳門元。<br />\n<br />\n案中被捕的兩名香港少年分別姓貝，18歲，無業；以及姓張，19歲，中學生；至於涉嫌販毒的13歲少女，為香港某中學一名中一生，由於未達到澳門的刑事歸責年齡16歲，因此司警沒有透露其姓氏。案中3人涉販毒已被送交檢察院處理。<br />\n<br />\n司警根據線報，昨晚7時許在漁翁街截獲目標的姓貝少年，相信他到澳門販毒已有一個月，司警在其他身上和租住酒店房間內檢獲48小包共重16.21克可卡因。疑人供稱受僱於香港犯罪集團來澳販毒，專向夜場人士埋手，每小包毒品售價600至800元，每包獲取100元作為佣金。司警追查後，發現貝昨晚原由販毒集團安排與兩名香港同黨進行毒品交收。<br />\n<br />\n司警即作部署，昨晚10時許在外港碼頭截獲兩名準備入境涉毒人士，竟發現兩人是香港的中學生，放學後變身「毒販」協助帶毒。其中只有13歲中一女學生在胸圍內被發現2包重約43.2克可卡因。女生落網後承認以每次3000元作為報酬，協助不法集團偷運毒品來澳，而一同被截獲的19歲姓張男中學生，則供稱負責監視運毒過程，每次收取500元報酬。而是次檢獲的毒品黑市價高達19萬元，而該名中一女學生則是司警自2015年起發現年齡最小的販毒人士。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180320/57972283\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180320%2F57972283&d=AViq3vxGpG8D50IWgIFLqDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=7a538c85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180320%2F57972283&h=b28ab24e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180320/57972283</a>"},{"pid":"a6a3b72994977a4dae9090cb99804d6b44c2dca8","tid":599432,"uid":64484,"like":127,"dislike":2,"score":125,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T11:52:33.000Z","msg":"驗下係咪處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4187204291908963e25499757833985f5fc985aa","tid":599432,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T11:53:04.000Z","msg":"60克 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151c180c67c232d6d880ddc6d08f033a68ebaef5","tid":599432,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T11:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f69ab2b51638bbceccfef092f53c2a8dea946c","tid":599432,"uid":59961,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T11:54:59.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"c34283393a453dde85f491968ad6437808a4e70c","tid":599432,"uid":61506,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T11:55:11.000Z","msg":"13歲好似唔洗入冊"},{"pid":"421a08f4d03d8050ba86be64320cfd6f1c5577d1","tid":599432,"uid":46943,"like":145,"dislike":1,"score":144,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T11:55:12.000Z","msg":"人仔細細咁大隻奶<br />\n揸揸先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d6f54964363f5484bea8bd07432a4b3dabd2dc","tid":599432,"uid":45165,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T11:55:18.000Z","msg":"咁算唔算墊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中一應該都無乜波"},{"pid":"d7ef9ada3ef0280091fa530bff492497cc00164d","tid":599432,"uid":52358,"like":69,"dislike":2,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T11:55:20.000Z","msg":"有乳香又可以賣貴啲<img s